headline: CME Group Completes Primary Conversion of 28-Day TIIE Interest Rate Swaps for Mexican Market
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced that it successfully converted approximately 42 trillion pesos (the equivalent of $2 trillion) in outstanding notional open interest from 28-day TIIE swaps to corresponding F-TIIE overnight index swaps (OIS) on November 22.
